data.description: You'll love this spacious ranch home with an open floor plan. The home is light, airy and leaves no concerns of feeling cramped. The large master bedroom features its own sitting room that is as big as the other bedrooms. The separate family room and living room gives plenty of room for entertaining. A separate man cave sports it's own pellet stove and is a great place to play cards or a round of darts! With almost 8 acres there is lots of room for animals and the new large shop fits plenty of vehicles!
